                    "type": "wait_action",
                    "step_category": "schedule",
                    "title": "行程安排槽位",
                    "text": "你刚才选中的课程已经进入下方 行程安排槽位。接下来继续安排课程，把本周 5 个槽位全部排满。当前你可以一边切 tab 挑课程，一边观察行程安排 的排课结果。",
                    "wait_action": "activity_schedule_full",
                    "target_scene": "activity",
                    "requires_scene": "activity",
                    "target_mode": "schedule_slots",
                    "focus_targets": [
                        {
                            "target_mode": "category_tabs",
                            "highlight_padding": 0
                        },
                        {
                            "target_mode": "activity_list",
                            "highlight_padding": 0
                        }
                    ],
                    "hide_until_scene_ready": true,
                    "skip_if_action_already_done": true,
                    "highlight_padding": 0
                },
                {
                    "id": "explain_main_story_slot",
                    "type": "wait_action",
                    "step_category": "schedule",
                    "title": "主线剧情占位槽",
                    "text": "这个带特殊边框和图标的槽位是主线剧情占位槽。它代表固定剧情事件，会自动保留在本周安排里，不属于玩家自由选课的普通课程槽位。",
                    "wait_action": "activity_click_main_event_slot",
