                    "text": "本周行程结算完成后，Luna 的属性变化都会汇总反映在这里。行程安排、日常互动都会持续影响这些属性，而这些属性也会进一步决定她未来的成长方向。现在点击左上角属性面板，继续下一步。",
                    "wait_action": "click_main_stats",
                    "target_scene": "main",
                    "requires_scene": "main",
                    "highlight_feature": "main.stats",
                    "hide_until_scene_ready": true,
                    "overlay_options": {
                        "capture_focus_clicks": true,
                        "focus_wait_action": "click_main_stats"
                    }
                },
                {
                    "id": "open_wechat_after_schedule",
